window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>When the mysterious Order comes to Mike Radley's home begging for his help, he doesn't know what to expect.</p> <p>He didn't expect a trip to Maui where he would butt heads with merfolk nobility.</p> <p>He really didn't expect a confrontation with the Captain, a man with a magical boat and mysterious goals.</p> <p>And he definitely didn't expect to get caught in a war between the living and the dead.</p> <p>Will Mike Radley sink the Captain's plans? Or will he drown in misery, instead?</p> <p>Welina mai i Hawaiʻi. Expect the Unexpected.</p>"; 
